description:
This is a 28 minute workout called 'PCOS Weight Loss Workout | Hormonal Imbalances, Irregular Periods (Beginner, Low Impact)' from the channel Akshaya Agnes.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
